   280→// ─── VISION ANALYSIS: Real video frame analysis with text fallback ─────
   281→// Primary: Upload frames to R2 → GPT-4o vision via Polsia proxy → NIM vision fallbacks
   282→// Fallback: Text-based LLM coaching from speech metrics (if ALL vision providers fail)
   283→async function analyzeVideoPresentation(frames, options = {}) {
